        "action": "Reduce ILR qualification to 7 years for long residence visa",
        "additional_details": "We think this would create a clearer, fairer pathway to settlement. We believe a single 7-year route gives stability, predictability, and equal treatment to all who live and contribute lawfully in the UK.",
        "background": "Reduce the qualifying period for Indefinite Leave to Remain under the long residence route from 10 years to 7 years.",
